<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Mesoveliidae. A. Mesoveloidea williamsi, macropterous male from Casimiro de Abreu / Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4342, −42.2934). B. Mesovelia amoena, apterous female from Macaé, Rio de Janeiro (−22.3171, −42.1900). C. Mesovelia bila, apterous male from Santa Maria Madalena, Rio de Janeiro (−21.87311, −41.92627). D. Mesovelia mulsanti, macropterous male from São Mateus, Espírito Santo (−18.7360, −39.7962). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437922>
    dc:description "FIGURE 35. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. A. Mesoveloidea williamsi. B. Mesovelia amoena. C. Mesovelia bila. D. Mesovelia mulsanti. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437922/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

